channel.title: Um Account is already logged in?
channel.description:
Some people before were complaining when they tried to log in, it said that they were alredy logged in. After a few attempts to fix the problem, I too am unable to log in without it saying I alredy am. I know I've seen this type of problem before, and sorry to bring it up again, but I just can't find it anywhere and I must get my server back on A.S.A.P Also This comes up in my runserver.
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 17 at ItemHandler.loadItemList(ItemHandler.java:39) at ItemHandler.<init>(ItemHandler.java:312) at server.main(server.java:34)
Yeah, so sorry again if its a bother :| but your help will be much appreciated, (as always :D )
Thanks again Hmpph
